  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The primary hypothesis of the investigators is that a virtual reality system combined with
      physical activity provided on a body weight support treadmill training would change clinical
      parameters of balance and mobility in people with Parkinson's Disease
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
